This paper discusses the ResNet architecture and its impact on deep neural networks, specifically in terms of norm preservation and optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also touches on topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL), which are less likely but still relevant.
